title: Christmas Tree Farm
description:
Taylor Swift grew up on a Christmas tree farm and envisioned another life for herself and honestly, same! Nick, Ana, Amy and Lacey reflect on their own dreams and think of what Taylor Swift should do next in her career!
We hope you all enjoy the holidays with those that you love! Thank you so much for listening! And reach out to us anytime! We love hearing your take on things!
